 However, it does not have an LCD built-in touchscreen display and it is slightly lighter than HERO+LCD. The HERO+ weighs 123 g whereas the HERO+LCD weighs 127 g. The housing also remained the same.\n\n====HERO5====\n[[File:Goprohero5actioncamerapoweredon.jpg|thumb|362x362px|A GoPro Hero 5 Action Camera. Powered on, not recording]]\nHERO5 Black and HERO5 Session were introduced in September 2016.<ref>[https://gopro.com/news/The-Launch-GoPro-Unveils-HERO5-and-Karma]</ref> They are waterproof up to 10 m, support 4K video recording at up to 30 fps and 1080p at up to 120 fps, automatic upload of footage to [[Cloud computing|cloud]] and voice controls.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Model !! HERO5 Session<ref>{{cite web|url=https://havecamerawilltravel.com/gopro/gopro-hero5-black-vs-hero5-session/ |title=GoPro HERO 5 Session vs HERO 5 Black &#124; Detailed Comparison Review & Specs |publisher=Havecamerawilltravel.com |date= |accessdate=2019-09-10}}</ref> !! HERO5 Black<ref name=\"dpreview1\">[https://www.dpreview.com/products/gopro/actioncams/gopro_hero_2018/specifications]</ref>\n|-\n!| Sensor Size\n| 1/2.3\" ||  1/2.3\"\n|-\n!| Aperture\n| {{f/|2.8}} || {{f/|2.8}}\n|-\n!| Dimensions\n|  38 x 38 x 36 mm || 62 x 45 x 33 mm\n|-\n!| Weight\n| 73 g || 118 g\n|-\n!| Video Modes \n| 4K30, 2.7K30, 1920x1440 @ 60p, 1080p90 || 4K30, 2.7K60, 1080p120, 720p240\n|-\n!| Video Formats\n| MP4 ([[H.264/MPEG-4 AVC|H.264]]) || MP4 ([[H.264/MPEG-4 AVC|H.264]])\n|-\n!| Stabilization\n| yes || yes \n|-\n!| Loop Recording\n| yes || yes\n|-\n!| Still Image Resolution \n| 10 MP || 12 MP\n|-\n!| Photo burst \n| 30 FPS || 30 FPS\n|-\n!| Connectivity \n| WiFi, Bluetooth || WiFi, Bluetooth, GPS\n|-\n!| Battery<ref name=\"bhphotovideo1\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bhphotovideo.com/c/product/1395242-REG/gopro_chdhb_501_hero_2018.html |title=GoPro HERO7 White Replacement for GoPro HERO 2018 &#124; B&H Photo |publisher=Bhphotovideo.com |date= |accessdate=2019-09-10}}</ref>\n| built-in 1000 mAh, Li-I