k%22|accessdate=2 November 2011 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WIF\">{{cite book |title=Operatsiia Groza, Ili, Oshibka V Tretem Znake: Istoricheskaia Khronika|last=Bunich |first=Igor |authorlink= |year=1994 |publisher=VITA-OBLIK |location= |isbn=978-5-85976-003-9  |page=88 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"czoczer150\">{{Cite book | first = Andrew J. | last = Crozier | title = The causes of the Second World War | publisher=Wiley-Blackwell | year = 1997 | isbn = 978-0-631-18601-4 | url = https://books.google.com/?id=S2hBXzB7XaYC&pg=PA150&lpg=PA150&printsec=8&dq=anti-comintern+Poland | pages = 150\u201351 | ref = harv }}.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"lawweb1\">{{cite web|url= http://avalon.law.yale.edu/subject_menus/ylbkmenu.asp |title =The Avalon Project: Documents in Law, History and Diplomacy |publisher=Yale |accessdate =11 January 2009}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"polishgovernment\">Ministry of Foreign Affairs. [http://www.ww2.pl/The,1939,Campaign,22.html The 1939 Campaign] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211211729/http://www.ww2.pl/The%2C1939%2CCampaign%2C22.html |date=11 December 2013 }} [[Polish Ministry of Foreign Affairs]], 2005.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"rothwell\">{{Cite book |first=Victor |last=Rothwell |title=Origins of the Second World War |publisher=Manchester University Press |year=2001 |isbn=978-0-7190-5958-2 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JLlaN3e4IcsC&pg=PA92#v=onepage&q&f=false |page= 92 |ref=harv}}</ref>\n}}\n\n== Sources ==\n{{Refbegin}}\n* {{cite journal |authorlink=Dariusz Baliszewski |last=Baliszewski |first=Dariusz |url= http://www.wprost.pl/ar/?O=68347 |title=Wojna sukces\u00f3w |journal=[[Wprost]] |issue=1141 |date=10 October 2004 |language=Polish |accessdate=24 March 2005 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal|authorlink=Dariusz Baliszewski |last=Baliszewski |first=Dariusz |url=http://www.wprost.pl/ar/?O=66711 |title=Most honoru |journal=[[Wprost]] |issue=1138 |date=19 September 2004 |language=Polish |accessdate=24 March 2005 |ref=harv |url-status=dead |archi